bbcode_text = "we tore bandages off too fast (too fast!) 
to watch red spread over pale yellow skin just because we couldwe cried tears in anger in euphoria
do not go gentle into that good light
turn off the night-light the firefly lights
and the streetlights at the end of all things
we were impervious

we dreamed in shouts and screams of elation no words needed
we were raw feeling bundled up into one party one mind
we bled blood red and laughed with our souls wide open
our eyes wide shut we ran mindlessly calloused soles pounding the floor and we ask you now
remember remember our deeds and our deaths
remember what we did
and that we, thereby you, truly did live once
"
