bbcode_text = "twelve eagles crowed our end (but we move too quickly to stop for you now)

winter in Martius have you ever thought
these months too long and years too short
where do unnamed days go to pass?

gilded limbo, limbs akimbo
sixty days make not an era
and hesitation is an unbecoming rouge
but haste is belladonna

you pass us by ten years ago tomorrow
we walk in different seasons
your footprints winterlight and timely
unwound, one-hundred years tick by out of sync and you
are back when we began"
