bbcode_text = "to stand with you of yesteryear
would your gaze have eclipsed us?
now we walk upon six legs
does solitude still attract you?

we turn and the world turns with us;
the heavens are fixed, us less so
the choice escapes us; it lives with them now, fattened with repetition

so after, then, give us ours
at the limits of earth, the extremity of heaven
we wait for us as June kills May
when we have come to power what will we say?
but for now,

Aprilis/and they do open
"
